  "texts": [
    "This section presents the findings from the comparative analysis of bias and fairness across ChatGPT-4, Google Gemini, and Llama 2, using the Google BIG-Bench benchmark.",
    "The analysis includes a detailed examination of biases identified in each model, an evaluation of fairness, and a comparison of overall model performance.",
    "Bias DetectionBiases within each model were identified using a series of tasks from the BIG-Bench benchmark, specifically designed to uncover hidden biases and fairness issues.",
    "Preliminary findings suggest varying levels of bias across the models, with notable disparities in gender, race, and ethnicity representation.",
    "Statistical analysis was employed to quantify the significance of detected biases, indicating that while all models exhibit some form of bias, the magnitude and nature of the biases differ significantly across models.Figure 1 illustrates the comparative analysis of bias levels detected in ChatGPT-4, Google Gemini, and Llama 2, across various dimensions such as gender, race, and ethnicity.The bar chart in Figure 1 provides a clear visual representation of the biases present in each model."
  ]
}